Mobs can be shown to wear armor and not drop any, yes. That is from model skins. It gives them the look of armor. But in order to have a weapon or shield or anything held and visible for that matter, they must have an actual item, and that item will drop from the corpse, unless it is a shopkeeper mob, then the corpse will poof.<br>
